snippet: The police opened fire in Indian Kashmir on Wednesday, killing one man as small groups opposed to Indian rule and the holding of national elections in the territory threw stones and attacked government vehicles.
lead_paragraph: The police opened fire in Indian Kashmir on Wednesday, killing one man as small groups opposed to Indian rule and the holding of national elections in the territory threw stones and attacked government vehicles.

headline.main: Police Kill 1 in Kashmir on Election Day
headline.print_headline: Police Kill 1 in Kashmir on Election Day
